        "creation_date": 1368057466,
        "body": "<p>That will be the SSL handshake taking the time. If Android supports <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/security/jsse/JSSERefGuide.html#Debug\" rel=\"nofollow\">javax.net.debug=ssl,handshake<\/a> you can see into it to learn more.<\/p>\n\n<p>But why are you using an anonymous cipher suite. Are you aware it's insecure?<\/p>\n",
